  "narrative": "### Node n2757: Procedure `saveText`\n\nThis procedure references symbols derived from its semantic block and symbol table.\n\n- **Raw sem JSON**:\n```json\n{}\n```",
  "rpgSnippet": "     P saveText        B\n     D saveText        PI\n     D*----------------------------------------------------------------\n       count = 1;\n       countZ = 0;\n       txt = *Blanks;\n       DoW count < 100;\n          Chain count HS1212ST;\n          If text = *Blanks;\n             exec sql\n                  delete from hsgptf\n                         where GPT_KZL = :G71000 and GPT_CNR = :G71050 and\n                               GPT_FNR = :G7306A AND GPT_ZNR = :count;\n          Else;\n             If countZ < 4;\n                countZ +=1;\n                txt(countZ) = TEXT;\n             EndIf;\n             exec sql\n                  update hsgptf set gpt_txt = :TEXT\n                         where GPT_KZL = :G71000 and GPT_CNR = :G71050 and\n                               GPT_FNR = :G7306A AND GPT_ZNR = :count;\n             If SQLCOD <> 0;\n                exec sql\n                     INSERT INTO HSGPTF\n                            (GPT_KZL, GPT_CNR, GPT_FNR, GPT_WNR, GPT_ZNR,\n                             GPT_TXT)\n                            VALUES(:G71000, :G71050, :G7306A, :G73065, :count,\n                                   :text);\n             EndIf;\n          EndIf;\n          count += 1;\n       EndDo;\n       G7312A = txt(1);\n       G7313A = txt(2);\n       G7332A = txt(3);\n       G7333A = txt(4);\n       exec sql\n            update hsg73pf set G73120 = :G7312A, G73130 = :G7313A,\n                               G73320 = :G7332A, G73330 = :G7333A\n                   where G73000 = :G71000 and G73050 = :G71050 and\n                         G73060 = :G7306A AND G73065 = :G73065;\n     P                 E",
